49
00:01:54,715 --> 00:01:57,463
It's going to be a very team
based collaborative exercise

50
00:01:57,463 --> 00:02:00,967
and we're going to plan at
the last responsible moment.

51
00:02:00,967 --> 00:02:03,400
And what that means is
that we are going to wait

52
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:06,103
